Package: AeRobiology
Type: Package
Title: A Computational Tool for Aerobiological Data
Version: 1.0.3
Author: Jes√∫s Rojo <Jesus.Rojo@uclm.es>, Antonio Picornell <picornell@uma.es>, Jose Oteros <OterosJose@gmail.com>
